Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:08.57,Monster,,0,0,0,,Your mommy abandoned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:12.78,Monster,,0,0,0,,You were thrown away like trash\Nalong with your drunk dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.41,Monster,,0,0,0,,Don't come out of\Nthe trash dump again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.93,Monster,,0,0,0,,\N{\fad(1000,0)}Chapter 70\N"The Town of Slaughter"\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.15,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm going to\Nhave to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.44,Monster,,0,0,0,,If you want to drink,\Ndo it after you pay your tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:20.66,Monster,,0,0,0,,If it's money...\NHere. This is for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.87,Monster,,0,0,0,,We don't have drinks to be bought\Nwith money earned by children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.45,Monster,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.04,Monster,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.01,Monster,,0,0,0,,He's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.55,Monster,,0,0,0,,You mean what happened\Nto Mr. Conrad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.51,Monster,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hillman's dog, too.\NCould it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.60,Monster,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have the guts\Nto shoot a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.81,Monster,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.23,Monster,,0,0,0,,He's just a drunk coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.16,Monster,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.87,Monster,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to\Nbe searching, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.37,Monster,,0,0,0,,Hey Merkel, let's call it a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.33,Monster,,0,0,0,,Hey, Merkel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.72,Monster,,0,0,0,,I found him ! I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.06,Monster,,0,0,0,,Merkel ! Mer–
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.69,Monster,,0,0,0,,Merkel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.71,Monster,,0,0,0,,This is Laufer!\NPlease respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.71,Monster,,0,0,0,,Someone !\NSomeone answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.60,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to\Ntake your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.24,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't have the guts\Nto shoot a gun.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.82,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.45,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just a drunk coward.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.78,Monster,,0,0,0,,The entire town,\Nit's full of corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.70,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's like a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.71,Monster,,0,0,0,,Wim...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.21,Monster,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Wim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.51,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NCalm down. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.68,Monster,,0,0,0,,I-I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.31,Monster,,0,0,0,,Calm down.\NNow let go of the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember.\NI shot them, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.11,Monster,,0,0,0,,They were teasing me...\Nso I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.62,Monster,,0,0,0,,Wim, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:04.71,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Calm down. It's all right.\NThere's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.68,Monster,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.60,Monster,,0,0,0,,Who did you get this gun from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.31,Monster,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.65,Monster,,0,0,0,,Laufer, I'm surprised you\Ngot this far on that leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.94,Monster,,0,0,0,,C-Call the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.73,Monster,,0,0,0,,The telephone doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,M-My gun was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.36,Monster,,0,0,0,,By someone in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.16,Monster,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He was an outsider\NI've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.58,Monster,,0,0,0,,Anyway, apply first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.50,Monster,,0,0,0,,Is he one of your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.92,Monster,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.18,Monster,,0,0,0,,How many of you\Nhave come to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.93,Monster,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.10,Monster,,0,0,0,,You've scattered quite\Na few guns around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:59.14,Monster,,0,0,0,,You've even given\Nthis child a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:00.98,Monster,,0,0,0,,Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.52,Monster,,0,0,0,,A gun? Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.73,Monster,,0,0,0,,"You're not trash."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.82,Monster,,0,0,0,,"Don't bother with them."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.61,Monster,,0,0,0,,"You were born for a reason."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:14.91,Monster,,0,0,0,,You told him those things\Nto encourage him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.96,Monster,,0,0,0,,He didn't shoot the gun.\NAll the bullets are still in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.17,Monster,,0,0,0,,Wim did just what\Nyou taught him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.89,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.64,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.14,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.90,Monster,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nthis town is filled with corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:57.70,Monster,,0,0,0,,How many guns did you\Nhand out in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.00,Monster,,0,0,0,,How many people\Ngot guns from you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.08,Monster,,0,0,0,,Don't make me any angrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.50,Monster,,0,0,0,,Terrible things happen\Nif you make me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.05,Monster,,0,0,0,,He looked just like\Nour grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:12.93,Monster,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:17.72,Monster,,0,0,0,,He looked just like\Nour dead grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.52,Monster,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.19,Monster,,0,0,0,,He knew us well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.44,Monster,,0,0,0,,It was as if he was\Nour real grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.19,Monster,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.86,Monster,,0,0,0,,You were writing a letter\Nto your dead grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.99,Monster,,0,0,0,,You were sending\Nhim information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.78,Monster,,0,0,0,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.08,Monster,,0,0,0,,He's probably after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.37,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm what he's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.21,Monster,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.67,Monster,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mr. Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:55.05,Monster,,0,0,0,,No. Franz...Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.69,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The heavy rain that continues\Nto fall in southern Germany{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.69,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has caused many casualties\Nalong the rivers in Bavaria.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.82,Monster,,0,0,0,,Hey, you smoke too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.32,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I've quit drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.70,Monster,,0,0,0,,You should quit smoking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.62,Monster,,0,0,0,,Dieter, what have you\Nbeen drawing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.96,Monster,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\NDoes it look like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.29,Monster,,0,0,0,,Look like whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.96,Monster,,0,0,0,,Like Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.25,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give that\Nto the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.88,Monster,,0,0,0,,They don't believe you\Nat the crucial moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.47,Monster,,0,0,0,,So I'll tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.10,Monster,,0,0,0,,"I'm talking about this man."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:48.15,Monster,,0,0,0,,"This man has gone off\Nto hunt monsters by himself."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.86,Monster,,0,0,0,,Tenma's going to\Ncome back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.82,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, a report on the damage.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.99,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Due to the Elgar River\Nflooding,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.33,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}roads have been\Nclosed in several areas.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.62,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both outbound and inbound railways\Nhave been shut down.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.12,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also, it's become\Ndifficult to get calls through{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.33,Monster,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to areas that have\Nexperienced power failures.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.96,Monster,,0,0,0,,This is an e-mail that\Ncame three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:17.38,Monster,,0,0,0,,After talking to Dr. Gillen, we decided\Nthat we should show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.05,Monster,,0,0,0,,Please show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.02,Monster,,0,0,0,,"To Nina..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.65,Monster,,0,0,0,,"I'll be waiting for you\Nin Ruhenheim."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.44,Monster,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.03,Monster,,0,0,0,,You think so too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:44.74,Monster,,0,0,0,,You described what Johan is trying\Nto do right now as "a perfect suicide."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.54,Monster,,0,0,0,,You said that lots of innocent people\Nare going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:52.96,Monster,,0,0,0,,Ruhenheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.34,Monster,,0,0,0,,There is a rural village with\Nthat name in southern Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.84,Monster,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that\NTenma has headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:01.93,Monster,,0,0,0,,I've got to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.76,Monster,,0,0,0,,Let me go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.85,Monster,,0,0,0,,It really is an odd feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:17.36,Monster,,0,0,0,,At first, you were someone who\Nexisted in a certain man's delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:22.95,Monster,,0,0,0,,Yes. You were like a character\Nin one of your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.83,Monster,,0,0,0,,For many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.87,Monster,,0,0,0,,I've carried out my investigation\Nby compiling objective data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:35.71,Monster,,0,0,0,,But this time, I ignored all my data\Nand followed that man's delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:40.01,Monster,,0,0,0,,As I tugged at the loose ends,\Npartially for fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.09,Monster,,0,0,0,,I met a young man\Nin the Czech Republic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.47,Monster,,0,0,0,,who visited Red Rose Mansion\Nvery often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.56,Monster,,0,0,0,,It was your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.60,Monster,,0,0,0,,This is a handwritten postcard\Nthat was sent to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.56,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's signed K. P. for Klaus Poppe,\Nyour real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:00.24,Monster,,0,0,0,,Even though I've arrived at this place\Nand you're right before my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,it still feels odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.41,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's as if a character from\Na picture book has sprung out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.45,Monster,,0,0,0,,But this is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:14.17,Monster,,0,0,0,,The list of Czech refugees in\Nthe late 80s that I looked up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.50,Monster,,0,0,0,,included the name\NKlaus Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.84,Monster,,0,0,0,,You fled here after\Nthe fall of the Berlin Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.18,Monster,,0,0,0,,What were you\Ntrying to run from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.39,Monster,,0,0,0,,People like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:36.61,Monster,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim was established\Nbecause of your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.53,Monster,,0,0,0,,I was created there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.24,Monster,,0,0,0,,Were you trying to run\Nfrom people like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:53.12,Monster,,0,0,0,,I know what he. ..what the man\Nnamed Johan is trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:58.92,Monster,,0,0,0,,And it's happening in\Nthis town right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.42,Monster,,0,0,0,,Another gunshot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.59,Monster,,0,0,0,,There were lots of dead people\Non the way to this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.35,Monster,,0,0,0,,What's happened\Nto this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.27,Monster,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get me out of\Nhere already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.73,Monster,,0,0,0,,I can't right now.\NAll transportation has been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.32,Monster,,0,0,0,,Jeez. What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.70,Monster,,0,0,0,,You go out and come back and\Ntake a shower each time you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:31.91,Monster,,0,0,0,,The town smells of gunpowder\Nand blood. It's sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:40.59,Monster,,0,0,0,,Now calm down. I've ordered\Nhot tea from the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.84,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NThere's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.06,Monster,,0,0,0,,Everything is going to disappear\Nwhen the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.48,Monster,,0,0,0,,"Disappear"? What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.36,Monster,,0,0,0,,All the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.32,Monster,,0,0,0,,I will let you go\Non two conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:14.04,Monster,,0,0,0,,You must go with Dr. Gillen...\NAnd you cannot bring a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.79,Monster,,0,0,0,,I don't need a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.00,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'll get ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:25.34,Monster,,0,0,0,,And. ..do what I told you\Nto do immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:31.72,Monster,,0,0,0,,Dieter, Eva, you Dr. Reichwein,\NMr. Schuwald, Karl and Lotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.18,Monster,,0,0,0,,Everyone that knows Johan\Nmust go into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,Johan is trying to erase\Nall his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.74,Monster,,0,0,0,,Come on.\NTry not to let Dieter see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.08,Monster,,0,0,0,,My memories with Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.50,Monster,,0,0,0,,My memories with you\NDr. Reichwein...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.75,Monster,,0,0,0,,My memories with\NLotte and Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.17,Monster,,0,0,0,,My memories with\Nthe Fortners...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.05,Monster,,0,0,0,,My memories with\NTenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.51,Monster,,0,0,0,,I have memories\NI don't want to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.27,Monster,,0,0,0,,Even if I have memories\NI want to erase...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.85,Monster,,0,0,0,,Johan is. ..\NJohan's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.73,Monster,,0,0,0,,...shouldn't be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.33,Monster,,0,0,0,,A police officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.79,Monster,,0,0,0,,His gun's been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.80,Monster,,0,0,0,,Don't move from that spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.23,Monster,,0,0,0,,Save this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.82,Monster,,0,0,0,,Who shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.61,Monster,,0,0,0,,There have been gunfights\Nall over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:15.78,Monster,,0,0,0,,First...several armed men\Ncame in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:22.46,Monster,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, the townspeople had\Nguns and were shooting at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.50,Monster,,0,0,0,,I've got to go and call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:32.13,Monster,,0,0,0,,I've got to at least\Nsave the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.01,Monster,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.02,Monster,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:51.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,The first time I heard\Nthat name was in 1995,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.78,Monster,,0,0,0,,in the statement of\Na certain neurosurgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.61,Monster,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:00.87,Monster,,0,0,0,,You admit that your deduction\Nis now incorrect?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:02.66,Monster,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:06.25,Monster,,0,0,0,,He's still a key witness to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.13,Monster,,0,0,0,,To me, Johan is still just a fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:17.68,Monster,,0,0,0,,"Fabrication"... I was obsessed by\Nthis term throughout my vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:22.68,Monster,,0,0,0,,What does a person who actually\Nexists have to do to become a fabrication?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.06,Monster,,0,0,0,,The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:31.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,Erase everyone who knows him and\Neveryone who knows about his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:36.91,Monster,,0,0,0,,In the end, Mr. Bonaparta, it'll be just\Nlike the ending of your picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.95,Monster,,0,0,0,,"At last he had\Nfound a name"'
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.91,Monster,,0,0,0,,"but there was no longer anyone\Naround to call him by it."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.79,Monster,,0,0,0,,"And Johan was such\Na wonderful name."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.55,Monster,,0,0,0,,If that's what's going to\Nhappen to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:18:01.35,Monster,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd do if I were Johan.\NI'm also a fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:05.85,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm not Newmeyer, the man\Nwhose name is written in the ledger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.31,Monster,,0,0,0,,nor am I Wolfgang Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.23,Monster,,0,0,0,,I am nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:19.66,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'll disappear with the person who\Ntook my memories and my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.41,Monster,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:28.71,Monster,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting here\Nfor my verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:37.67,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid to die. But I don't\Nknow how to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.10,Monster,,0,0,0,,But I will accept everything that\Nhappens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.77,Monster,,0,0,0,,You've been waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.52,Monster,,0,0,0,,You're not afraid to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:52.61,Monster,,0,0,0,,Do you know how terrible\Nthe things you did were?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:57.49,Monster,,0,0,0,,Do you know what it means to destroy\Nthe root of good and evil in a person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:02.37,Monster,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happens when\Nyou awaken the monster within people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:09.21,Monster,,0,0,0,,People... People should think\Nthat meals taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.25,Monster,,0,0,0,,They should look forward\Nto picnics on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.80,Monster,,0,0,0,,They should think that a beer\Nafter work tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.34,Monster,,0,0,0,,People should...\NPeople should...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:25.72,Monster,,0,0,0,,feel sad from the bottom of\Ntheir hearts if their child dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.14,Monster,,0,0,0,,I won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get you\Nout of this town safely
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.69,Monster,,0,0,0,,and have you make\Neverything public.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.32,Monster,,0,0,0,,You're going to\Nreveal to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.40,Monster,,0,0,0,,the identity of the monster\Nthat you awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.87,Monster,,0,0,0,,Until then, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.46,Monster,,0,0,0,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.63,Monster,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:20:01.05,Monster,,0,0,0,,Someone's behind this massacre.\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.51,Monster,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.39,Monster,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.93,Monster,,0,0,0,,Another gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.32,Monster,,0,0,0,,Is someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:27.91,Monster,,0,0,0,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.04,Monster,,0,0,0,,Look. I'm not holding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.88,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NThere's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.60,Monster,,0,0,0,,I've come to help you. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.35,Monster,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.02,Monster,,0,0,0,,Get out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.94,Monster,,0,0,0,,Don't cry! I'll take you to\Nthe path through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.11,Monster,,0,0,0,,You can run, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:10.16,Monster,,0,0,0,,Th-There's a man giving orders\Nfrom the Hotel Bergbach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.41,Monster,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.63,Monster,,0,0,0,,Even so,\Nthis is my only gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.75,Monster,,0,0,0,,These two were outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.84,Monster,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:25.30,Monster,,0,0,0,,This all happened because\NI won the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.81,Monster,,0,0,0,,If only we had informed the police\Nearlier that we found Conrad's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.81,Monster,,0,0,0,,Before the town\Nwent mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.02,Monster,,0,0,0,,You bought these?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.49,Monster,,0,0,0,,I-I haven't fired a single shot!\NHonest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:49.07,Monster,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this one\Nand this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.12,Monster,,0,0,0,,You protect this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:52.95,Monster,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:56.29,Monster,,0,0,0,,Even ordinary citizens\Nare carrying guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:59.25,Monster,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective.\NI can tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:02.46,Monster,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:07.43,Monster,,0,0,0,,Let me buy you a beer\Nwhen this job is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:10.85,Monster,,0,0,0,,Yes, please...a good beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:15.77,Monster,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:19.06,Monster,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.81,Monster,,0,0,0,,Please, live!
